---
title: Pork Larb over Jade Rice with Crispy Green Beans and Crushed Peanuts
description: Green beans won’t be the only green item on your plate tonight. We put our own spin on larb, a spicy meat salad popular in Laos and Thailand, by serving ground pork over green jade rice. The secret to its stunning hue? Bamboo juice. It lends a floral aroma and magazine-worthy finish to this unique dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-pork-larb-2892f2e2.jpg
